<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-15-0609 </DOCNO><TEXT>We investigate an oil company's optimal depletion of oil and gas reservoirs,taking into account that the depletion policy itself influences the recoverablereserves (recovery factor) and that we have up-front capital costs. Thedepletion policy is defined by the amount of investment in productionand in injection projects. 6 refs., 8 figs., 2 tabs.</TEXT></DOC>